    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Starting at 2nd level, you can use your Channel Divinity to mark another creature's life force for termination.</p><p>As an action, you choose one creature you can see within 30 feet of you, cursing it until the end of your next turn. The next time you or an ally of yours deals damage to the cursed creature, the creature has vulnerability to all of the source's damage, and then the curse ends.</p><p>If the creature has immunity to the damage type, then it is treated as having resistance instead.</p>",
